
<div class="hero">
    <h1>Create your own board game <br>to  manage your games </h1>
    <h3>Managing your games has never been so easy.<br>
    Try our board game manager and you won't be able to do without it !</h3>
    <%= link_to "I CREATE MY BOARD GAME", new_user_session_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
  </div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="features">
    <h2>How can we help you ?</h2>
    <div class="home-features">

      <div class="feature">
        <%= image_tag("Homepage/save.png", style: "height:200px;margin-bottom:20px;") %>
        <p>You can <span class="highlight"> save all your your game sessions </span>in
        infinite games for all your games. Even even those that do not belong to you.  </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <%= image_tag("Homepage/quest.png", style: "height:200px; margin-bottom:20px;") %>
        <p>You can <span class="highlight">find the ideal board game for your party </span>in your
        library games, in that of your friends or in the infinite games library.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <%= image_tag("Homepage/stat.png", style: "height:200px;margin-bottom:20px;") %>
        <p>You can <span class="highlight">see your session game statistics </span>for each game you have played.
        You will know who is the best to play, how many games you play in the year, ...  </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="search">
  <div class="search-title">
    <%= image_tag("dice-search.png") %>
    <h2>Find your ideal board game !</h2>
    <%= image_tag("dice-search.png") %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="games-month">
<h2>Infinite Games of the month </h2>
  <%= link_to "SEE ALL THE BOARD GAMES", games_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
